; [F] testing machinery ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾\ {{{1

    ; used for removing indent upto and including «|» in strings like:
    ; "func
    ;       |  1.0
    ;       |  -1.0"
    (def:: str => str
        wystrip [wy_code]
        (re_sub r"\n\s+\|" "\n" wy_code))

    (defmacro wy_str_test [a b] `(assertm eq (w2h (wystrip ~a)) (wystrip ~b)))

